fields.question_text:
For the function

\[f(x) = \begin{cases}
    \left\lvert{x + 6}\right\rvert & \text{if } x \leq 5 \\
    - x^{2} + 37 & \text{if } x > 5
\end{cases}\]  

Find $\displaystyle\lim_{x \to 5^+ } f(x)$

For the function

\[f(x) = \begin{cases}
    \left\lvert{x + 6}\right\rvert & \text{if } x < 5 \\
    - x^{2} + 37 & \text{if } x \geq 5
\end{cases}\]  

Find $\displaystyle\lim_{x \to 5^- } f(x)$

For the function

\[f(x) = \begin{cases}
    \left\lvert{x + 4}\right\rvert & \text{if } x \leq 3 \\
    - x^{2} + 17 & \text{if } x > 3
\end{cases}\]  

Find $\displaystyle\lim_{x \to 3^+ } f(x)$
